OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe chance
OL,6,Fof a few showers this evening. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Fvariable cloud and some lengthy clear
OL,9,Fperiods.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMany places will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome bright intervals, although
OL,13,Fcloudier across western Tayside with a
OL,14,Ffew showers.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,17,FScattered showers on Tuesday, slow
OL,18,Fmoving and heavy by afternoon. Drier
OL,19,Fon Wednesday with fewer showers. Early
OL,20,Frain on Thursday then dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
